                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Pearson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Teheran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-12-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 12, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Pearson reports that the Persian minister for foreign affairs informs him
                    that the Persian Government will immediately pay the indemnity of $50,000 gold,
                    but begs the President to reduce the amount of the indemnity.)</p>
            </div>
